{"tid":2322960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"許智峯：美國國務卿辦公室主動聯絡  了解滙豐一事","createTime":"2020-12-12T18:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T07:14:38.000Z","uid":227801,"like":190,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"2e64a5aa875aa51a74275e039c3972cd50652fbd","tid":2322960,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T18:26:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201213/P5YV57L2EZAWFLOMJDWTZBG3X4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201213%2FP5YV57L2EZAWFLOMJDWTZBG3X4%2F&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcn4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=28e7831d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201213%2FP5YV57L2EZAWFLOMJDWTZBG3X4%2F&h=663a03a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201213/P5YV57L2EZAWFLOMJDWTZBG3X4/</a><br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n美國務卿辦公室主動聯絡了解滙豐凍結戶口一事<br />\n<br />\n身在英國的他希望能與其他流亡海外的人士，齊將香港帶上國際社會的議程。他認為要爭取外國政府把制裁面拉闊，不只是集中制裁官員，而是要一併制裁配合政權凍結他戶口的滙豐銀行、管理層和香港監管機構，以懲罰他們助紂為虐：「我係公開呼籲制裁滙豐。」他又指，美國國務卿辦公室日前主動聯絡他，了解滙豐凍結他戶口一事，但對方未有明言有何行動。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"3637afca1e00da5a4ca30b1c42d5bd67861b328d","tid":2322960,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T18:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"136a3ce94787b9906fd87d5236ca3064ce1a1a58","tid":2322960,"uid":327169,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T18:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  molamolamola 大貓銀行完喇!"},{"pid":"ee5a090f7d8011717c30612606ad5791ddd09fcf","tid":2322960,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":46,"score":-46,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T18:29:45.000Z","msg":"反而中